node.text: Introducing Soft Matte Primer. A lightweight makeup primer with a transformative water-gel texture that creates a soft-matte finish. Featuring NARS’ exclusive Climate Balancing Technology to help control the appearance of shine, maintain makeup wear, and balance skin in any climate. Available exclusively @sephora.
